| FR-012 | PENDING 可取消，FAILED 可重试；FAILED 重试保留原 `taskId` 审计链路并递增执行尝试次数；EXECUTING 取消按批次边界收口并最终置为 `CANCELED` | cancel / retry API | CANCELED / PENDING / FAILED / EXECUTING | `POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/cancel`、`POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/retry` | contract / api / backend / verify | `docs/testing/test-matrix.md` / `docs/testing/verify-matrix.md` / `docs/testing/ACCEPTANCE_EXAMPLES.md` | `AC-012`、`AC-E015`、`state-matrix.yaml` | 取消和重试状态机容易被误返回内部标记 |
| FR-013 | 创建幂等、执行尝试、DB 锁租约和任务配置快照必须形成同一条审计链路；锁租约默认 5 分钟，接管延续当前 `attemptNo`，FAILED 重试才递增 `attemptNo` | create API + Scheduler + task snapshot | default / conflict / processing / error | create API、Scheduler、snapshot 契约 | contract / scheduler / backend / verify | `docs/testing/test-matrix.md` / `docs/testing/verify-matrix.md` / `docs/testing/ACCEPTANCE_EXAMPLES.md` | `difficulty-research.md`、`requirement-interface-matrix.md`、`state-matrix.yaml` | 幂等冲突、锁接管和快照沿用是最容易漏证据的区域 |
| FR-014 | 采购订单样板必须覆盖创建时间范围、订单状态、供应商、采购组织、关键词、游标分页、敏感字段、空数据、分片、权限、审计、下载和 10 万行压测证据 | purchase-order query template + platform export flow | default / empty / long_content / error | 采购订单样板契约 | contract / backend / query / file / verify | `docs/testing/test-matrix.md` / `docs/testing/verify-matrix.md` / `docs/testing/ACCEPTANCE_EXAMPLES.md` | `AC-017`、`AC-018`、`AC-E022`、`AC-E023` | 样板合同是实现前最关键的可执行证据 |

